{"id":"5b2d653e-06f2-4184-b0f5-c658f05abb52","name":"Simon Riley","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">AnyPOV Small Demi-human User × Annoyed Ghost</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 95, 119)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(249, 198, 199); color: inherit\">Requested by the amazing @Ikee_raynott</mark></strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_0731ea42-1596-4e42-82d5-ae4600b62dfd.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_79146da6-2320-4a0f-992c-5c3824aaeaff.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_11fb06f0-508b-4320-83a1-c953e9b5dd67.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">The last thing that Simon wanted to deal with after coming home from a mission was a sneaky little thief roaming around his flat eating and drinking his groceries, but luckily he's managed to find the small culprit in the act.</mark></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_a51f8bd5-09e3-4ba1-9811-76ea438c392c.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_ccbb0885-0b9f-4a1e-ac33-adbabb4fa8c6.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4151e4bd-6243-4e85