text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 198, 199)\">I test my bots using the JLLM (I'm a broke bish so I can't afford any other API's), so if you use another API make sure to comment on the bot you are using and let me know how it's perform","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4151e4bd-6243-4e85-a55d-285c3b22a74a_f176cb42-ae62-483e-8b52-7d78bb27c387.webp","creator":"TinyLuma","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","😂 Comedy","🌗 Switch"],"chats":5421,"messages":65420,"created_at":"2024-06-28T14:53:44.513393+00:00"}